<frame w="*" h="*" bg="#F6FFE3" gravity="center">
	<vertical>
		<horizontal marginTop="0" bg="#18181C" gravity="center">
			<text textStyle="bold" textColor="#EA5217" textSize="26sp">
				{Name1}
			</text>
			<text marginRight="5" textStyle="bold" textColor="#08BFF5" textSize="26sp">
				{Name2}
			</text>
			<text textStyle="bold" textColor="#FC03FC" textSize="31sp">
				{Name3}
			</text>
			<text textStyle="italic" textColor="#869093" textSize="26sp">
				{Name4}
			</text>
		</horizontal>
	</vertical>
	<ScrollView>
		<vertical marginTop="30">
			<vertical marginLeft="30" marginRight="30" marginTop="40">
				<horizontal gravity="center">
					<vertical marginRight="30">
						<Switch id="autoService" text="无障碍服务" textStyle="bold" textColor="#000000" textSize="16sp" checked="{{auto.service!=null}}" />
					</vertical>
					<vertical>
						<Switch id="consoleShow" text="控制台悬浮窗" textStyle="bold" textColor="#000000" textSize="16sp" checked="true" />
					</vertical>
				</horizontal>
				<vertical marginTop="140">
					<text text="关键词" textStyle="bold" textColor="#000000" textSize="16sp" />
					<text text="关键词之间用逗号分隔" textColor="red" />

					<horizontal marginTop="14" gravity="left">
						<input text="" gravity="left" inputType="textImeMultiLine" id="keywords" w="*" />
					</horizontal>

					<text text="指定评论内容" textStyle="bold" textColor="#000000" textSize="16sp" />
					<horizontal marginTop="14" gravity="left">
						<input text="" gravity="left" inputType="useComment" id="keywords" w="*" />
					</horizontal>

					<text text="每词评论次数" textStyle="bold" textColor="#000000" textSize="16sp" />
					<horizontal marginTop="0" gravity="left">
						<input lines="1" maxLength="6" inputType="number" id="commentCountLimit" w="60" gravity="left" />
					</horizontal>
					<horizontal marginTop="14" gravity="center" w="*" h="*">
						<button id="save" marginLeft="10" marginRight="20" bg="#23A9F2" text="保存" />
						<button id="boot" marginLeft="20" marginRight="10" bg="#23A9F2" text="启动" />
					</horizontal>
					<vertical marginTop="130" marginLeft="20">
						<text>
						</text>
						<text>
							1. 开启无障碍
						</text>
						<text>
							2. 注意：开启悬浮窗，可以避免被系统杀掉。
						</text>
						<text>
							3. 填入关键词，并以逗号分隔，中英文逗号都可以
						</text>
						<text>
							4. 启动
						</text>
						<text>
		注意：在第一次运行不会显示日志控制台。而在之后，才会显示。因为，控制台需要用第一次来确定，日志窗口的位置。智能避开关键元素
						</text>
					</vertical>
				</vertical>
			</vertical>
		</vertical>
	</ScrollView>
</frame>
